abstract: Norway's Aksel Lund Svindal wins super-G World Cup event in Kitzbuhel, Austria, extending Norway's World Cup winning streak to five races.
snippet: Aksel Lund Svindal mastered a tricky super-G course in Kitzbühel, Austria, to extend Norway’s World Cup winning streak to five races.
lead_paragraph: Aksel Lund Svindal mastered a tricky super-G course in Kitzbühel, Austria, to extend Norway’s World Cup winning streak to five races.
